

Number 1

Algorithm for making a Cup of Tea with Conditional Statements e.g (if/else  loop)

Step1- Get a cup of Kettle
Step2- Fill the Kettle with water
Step3- Start to heat the water
Step4- While the water is not yet boiling, continue to heat (loop)
Step5- Get a Cup of Tea
Step6- Get a bag of Tea
Step7- Place a bag of tea into the tea cup
Step8- Pour the boiling water into the cup of tea
Step9- Wait 4minutes for farmentation, and remove the bag of tea
Step10- (if/else Condition): If the person wants sweetner, then add sweetner
                             else ignore sweetner
Step11- Add cream milk
Step 12- Serve the cup of tea
